{"tid":307941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"神駒《主能夠》有對手！新華社神曲無粒字啱音  侮辱粵語！","createTime":"2017-07-03T17:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T17:07:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47c5ab1d4cbc17f69b624d6fbe97dbb97b263ade","tid":307941,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170703/large/1499085549_1379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170703%2Flarge%2F1499085549_1379.jpg&h=b8ec39f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毒果段片:<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170704/56909914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170704%2F56909914&d=omeP7BZpcxedT4OJKrQBIP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a857c5a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170704%2F56909914&h=7d871283\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170704/56909914</a><br />\n<br />\n新華社為唱好香港回歸20周年，再度推出「神曲」，但廣東話版完全不合音，被網民瘋狂嘲笑，音樂人周博賢亦在facebook發帖狠批，直言「初聽好笑，再聽好嬲！」<br />\n<br />\n他又解釋，廣東話有九聲，句子中字與字之間有相對的高低音，如旋律並不符合這些音調的高低，便會出現「唔啱音」的情況，故若先有旋律，便要選擇符合旋律高低音調的字的組合，才可填進去，「否則唱出嚟係唔知唱乜；that's why 填廣東詞咁難！」<br />\n<br />\n周博賢直斥這首呢首歌《我的Hong Kong》是對廣東話的侮辱，完全無視廣東話自古以來已確立的規律，無視香港人對廣東話既有的概念同認知，結果成了走樣變形的歌詞，「一國兩制，港人治港」成了「日國兩劑，鋼孕之肛」，「呢首歌彷彿清楚話俾我哋知，係咁㗎喇，中央係唔會理你甚麼既有概念同認知，我說了便算，包括甚麼是法治、一國兩制、港人治港、三權分立、特首超然、以至甚麼是廣東話！That's why越聽越嬲！」<br />\n<br />\n他又說曲中重手地使用的Autotune（自動調諧），將走音變成合音，有如人大釋法的力度，「又係嘅，唔啱主旋律嘅，咪出重手（釋法也好，強力部門也好）調返正囉&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"0f79a9a272f981a559f0ddf2599d23002025ab91","tid":307941,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">新華社推《我的Hong Kong》粵語版　周博賢：得「I Believe啱音」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n新華社早前趁住香港回歸20周年，推出了一首「神曲」，用半Rap半唱的形式介紹「一國兩制」。原來，新華社在7月1日當天又再獻新猷，推出《我的Hong Kong》的粵語版，並由港區人大代表、民建聯成員並有「愛國歌手」之稱的張明敏，聯同兒子傾情演唱。新華社還形容此歌是「國社神曲」。<br />\n<br />\n全曲長3分35秒，一聽以為是普通話歌，有點「聖詩」或「校歌」的感覺，細心聽才聽得出是廣東話，有網民留言指「似乎唔多啱音」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/680120/xlarge/cf226d647d99a58485e0156474a64e6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F680120%2Fxlarge%2Fcf226d647d99a58485e0156474a64e6a.jpg&h=906cd7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新華社推出粵語版的《我的Hong Kong》，MV用上簡體字展示歌詞。(截圖自《我的Hong Kong》MV)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">周博賢：得「I Believe啱音」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n音樂人周博賢指，剛聽到時感覺「好好笑」，因歌詞通通「唔啱音」，但後來對此感氣憤，覺得廣東話歌被侮辱，「廣東話有九聲，其實好難填，因為字本身有佢嘅音、字與字之間有相對高低，如要放入旋律，要與九聲配合先至啱音」，此歌卻無視廣東話特質，將其「硬塞」進歌曲中，「變形走樣嘅廣東歌，就好似變形走樣嘅一國兩制。」"},{"pid":"a52825d5ec35131f1f3e6ec469a7d1fc7418a27f","tid":307941,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:49:32.000Z","msg":"香港回歸20周年的日子將至，內地官媒新華社在本港Facebook專頁推出「粵語神歌」，配合動畫發佈歌曲，以廣東話、半「rap」半唱形式推銷一國兩制，部分歌詞提及20年前回歸當日，「降落咗屈辱，升起咗主權」，又大唱「最愛紫荊加襯紅色的底，載滿底氣作為內心依歸」，字幕全為簡體字，長約3分47秒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/667054/xlarge/bc3840c3798fda09798cb02865e6a56c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F667054%2Fxlarge%2Fbc3840c3798fda09798cb02865e6a56c.jpg&h=ec43a2d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地官媒新華社在本港Facebook專頁推出「粵語神曲」，以廣東話、半「rap」半唱形式推銷一國兩制。（新華社片截圖）<br />\n內地官媒新華社今日（27日）早上在本港Facebook專頁首推出「粵語神曲」，以廣東話唱出一國兩之歌，並配合動畫演釋。動畫場境設定為課室，片中教師稱要考學生關於一國兩制，學生即回應道：「觸碰我知識嘅盲區。」<br />\n<br />\n然後有男聲以「超高速」讀出一國兩制的定義，又「rap」出「國家授權畀香港嘅大禮包入面」，有行政管理權、立法權、獨立司法及終審權；亦提到香港發展、基建及國策「一帶一路快車道」等。<br />\n<br />\n部分歌曲提到「最愛紫荊加襯紅色的底，載滿底氣作為內心依歸，完美紫荊融入五星永不褪，閃閃星際最耀眼之最」；內容又加插1997年7月1日回歸升旗片段，「降落咗屈辱，升起咗主權，升起嘅係我堂堂嘅主權」。歌曲由北京正本源文化有限公司制作。"},{"pid":"6f01fc6f4fbb9634ff1219617dc7fcdbe12da844","tid":307941,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4044ec5aabb54fd3cfdd855fc419b7f469643ed9","tid":307941,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T18:25:17.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc2b0c07e6b3839376cefd139096d798d7dd94f","tid":307941,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722dd33b86b6e710d6a4fa3e08e3d349ef6db93c","tid":307941,"uid":86943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T18:37:33.000Z","msg":"主撚狗同佢比真係車尾燈都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92df525c71ab2e39db22557a5b605ae5e223dbd9","tid":307941,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:43:19.000Z","msg":"神駒都唔夠佢柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3414195682024b8677be15470e5257d7fc109558","tid":307941,"uid":601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我聽左啲咩"},{"pid":"b6773c1bc3d806a4e7b2c7b62826348f96178cdd","tid":307941,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"我的Hong Kong<br />\nMy香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a83ed1e2fe6aec1ac3cecbfa911098bbb119bb2","tid":307941,"uid":80966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:44:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de5603eab90b7d59d25fadfbaa4a09b84a9b3b6e","tid":307941,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:49:29.000Z","msg":"煮撚鳩"},{"pid":"c1b2fca4045d895ecb297674a4ee9561ca6624ef","tid":307941,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:57:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37674f6c9c17f45aa09c7c316dc9e30589ae3927","tid":307941,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"製作費被剋扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？咁多奶共大明星你唔去搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893121b6e89751701c09924bc60881adb023b6ce","tid":307941,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"好洗腦佢既詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5090616d0ec4a3aa3867755fea1cc1e70af3338","tid":307941,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T02:06:36.000Z","msg":"應該係普通話來"},{"pid":"aa30c101313db97ca6d4b9f8969955f212185443","tid":307941,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T02:34:24.000Z","msg":"lm 陣間聽"},{"pid":"a4554e80be33dd8a425719ef63d7c8ecf549464e","tid":307941,"uid":62409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T02:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/68230_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F68230_WM.jpg&h=e1dae19c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12bab0e37ae93573f4ff5a6f28afbdb4b0579f23","tid":307941,"uid":45650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"香港個名真係徹底俾中國強姦再強姦"},{"pid":"cb8a870a6d38ff33dbf3b52ee5d1a2491792b507","tid":307941,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/68230_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F68230_WM.jpg&h=e1dae19c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7655ed7672ea911206a6d96c697d6d96a91ad922","tid":307941,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481ecdde2dec0128973ee193d47ff288a9d6aed5","tid":307941,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"同呢個有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9z8meqvsQo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz9z8meqvsQo&d=omeP7BZpcxedT4OJKrQBIP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e54a1a9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9z8meqvsQo</a>"},{"pid":"64791741aa78f4f2d5cfeffe9053878c16034332","tid":307941,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同呢個有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9z8meqvsQo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz9z8meqvsQo&d=omeP7BZpcxedT4OJKrQBIP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e54a1a9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9z8meqvsQo</a></blockquote><br />\n哩個起碼都有半句啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5907074b8e9226254a500b7a120850ad84d93bf0","tid":307941,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:26:17.000Z","msg":"點解qbear唔會有呢種感覺"},{"pid":"d5d9ffc15955d4b562d041444e934e577b14bddd","tid":307941,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解qbear唔會有呢種感覺</blockquote><br />\nQbea